    h1 About Downtown Donuts

    p Downtown Donuts is a small, family-owned donut and coffee shop that has been serving the downtown community since 1992.

    p The goal of this redesign is to make the business feel modern and easy to access online while still keeping the cozy, local feeling of the shop.

    p The website helps customers view the menu, find ordering options, learn the story of the business, and leave comments about their experience.

    article.card
      h2 Our Mission
      p We want every customer to feel welcome, whether they are stopping in before work, ordering breakfast for a group, or grabbing coffee with a friend.